### =============================================================================
### ATLAS FOOD — SURVEY MANAGEMENT (ADMIN)
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

# Auth credentials untuk admin test
# Harus cocok dengan ADMIN_SEED_* di .env
@adminEmail = admin@mail.com
@adminPassword = Password123!
@adminName = Admin Atlas

# Dynamic Token (Otomatis terisi setelah Login)
@adminAccessToken = {{login.response.body.data.access_token}}

### =============================================================================
### SETUP: Register & Login Admin
### =============================================================================

### 1. Login Admin (gunakan akun seed, bukan register)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###

### =============================================================================
### SURVEY MANAGEMENT TESTS
### =============================================================================

### 3. Create Survey
# @name createSurvey
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Survey Gizi SD Kelas 5 2024",
  "description": "Pengumpulan data gizi siswa kelas 5 SD",
  "meals_config": [
    { "name": "Sarapan", "time": "06:00-08:00", "order": 1 },
    { "name": "Snack Pagi", "time": "09:00-10:00", "order": 2 },
    { "name": "Makan Siang", "time": "11:00-13:00", "order": 3 },
    { "name": "Snack Sore", "time": "15:00-16:00", "order": 4 },
    { "name": "Makan Malam", "time": "18:00-20:00", "order": 5 }
  ],
  "prompts": {
    "welcome": "Selamat datang di survey gizi kami",
    "instructions": "Silakan pilih waktu makan dan makanan yang Anda konsumsi"
  },
  "start_date": "2024-01-01",
  "end_date": "2024-12-31",
  "status": "draft"
}

###

### 4. List All Surveys
# @name listSurveys
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Get Survey Detail (gunakan ID dari response create survey)
# @name getSurvey
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys/{{createSurvey.response.body.data.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. Update Survey
# @name updateSurvey
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys/{{createSurvey.response.body.data.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Survey Gizi SD Kelas 5 2024 - UPDATED",
  "status": "active",
  "description": "Pengumpulan data gizi siswa kelas 5 SD - Updated"
}

###

### 7. Clone Survey
# @name cloneSurvey
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys/{{createSurvey.response.body.data.id}}/clone
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 8. Delete Survey
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys/{{createSurvey.response.body.data.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### ERROR TEST CASES
### =============================================================================

### 9. Create Survey tanpa meals_config (harus error)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Survey tanpa meals",
  "meals_config": []
}

###

### 10. Get Survey dengan ID invalid (harus 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys/invalid-survey-id
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 11. Create Survey tanpa Authorization (harus 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Survey tanpa auth",
  "meals_config": [
    { "name": "Sarapan", "time": "06:00", "order": 1 }
  ]
}

###

### =============================================================================
### PUBLIC RESPONDENT SURVEY FLOW (USING ACCESS TOKEN)
### =============================================================================

### 12. Activate Survey (ubah status ke active untuk respondent test)
# @name activateSurvey
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/surveys/{{createSurvey.response.body.data.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active"
}

###

# Ambil access_token dari response activateSurvey
@surveyAccessToken = {{activateSurvey.response.body.data.access_token}}

### 13. Get Survey dengan Access Token (public - tanpa auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/surveys/{{surveyAccessToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### 14. Join Survey dengan Access Token (public - tanpa auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/surveys/{{surveyAccessToken}}/join
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### 15. Get Survey dengan Access Token Invalid (harus 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/surveys/invalid-access-token-12345
Accept: application/json

###

### 16. Join dengan Access Token Invalid (harus 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/surveys/invalid-access-token-12345/join
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###
